    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster with no chips or scratches, and the interior is completely flawless, smelling like new. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all service records up to date and no signs of wear. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered.",
