    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is ready for a new owner who values functionality over perfection. The engine is reliable and the car is fully drivable, though there are some minor oil leaks typical for its age and the transmission shows some occasional hesitation. Inside, the cabin shows noticeable wear, including some fading on the upholstery and minor scratches on the dashboard. The exterior has several small dents and some paint chips, but the body remains structurally sound. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a dependable workhorse or a budget-friendly daily driver that may require some minor maintenance down the road.",
