      "description": "Ready to hit the road in style? This well-maintained beauty is in great shape and looking for its next adventure! It runs smoothly and has been cared for consistently, making it a reliable choice for anyone seeking a solid, high-quality ride without the brand-new price tag. You'll love how it handles!",
