    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every aspect of this motorcar has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. With flawless aesthetics and peerless mechanical integrity, this acquisition is tailored for the discerning collector who demands nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
